                <h3>Host an Exchange Student</h3>
                <h6>
                    A host family for a Rotary exchange student, you assume parental responsibility for this young ambassador from another country, to provide shelter and sustenance,
                    guidance and counsel, and love and support to the child of strangers who may live thousands of miles from you. They have their own insurance and pocket money
                    - you will offer room and board. We do not pay any stipend to host families.
                <br>
                <br>
                    Rotary Clubs are always looking for potential host families.
                </h6>
              </div>
